```
SimpleDateFormat formatter = new SimpleDateFormat("dd-MM-yyyy");
Date myDate = new Date(233276400000L);
Date parsedDate = formatter.parse("24-05-1977");
assertEquals(myDate.getTime(), parsedDate.getTime());
```

